{
  "stem": "71.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And a black wagon drove into the cemetery, and we heard two shots.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And maybe five, ten minutes later, that black wagon went out-- left the cemetery-- and they told us we can go back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Later we found out that there were two brothers that used to give out to the Germans Jew-- names of Jewish people who had money, or had something.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they didn't want to leave them, so they wouldn't tell the world what the Germans were doing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they killed them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They shot them on the cemetery and they were buried there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that's what the Germans did with all the people that, you know, used to bring all the information to them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They used to kill them after that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Germans, once they came in-- they used to come in in the morning-- to get people, to send them out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by 5 o'clock, they used to leave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So everybody used to come out like, from, from the basements.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, the worms come out from the, the-- and people started cooking and preparing some-- whatever they cook, food or something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One day, at 5 o'clock, my little sister-- should rest in peace-- went outside, and she heard-- overheard two policemen saying that they were called to the station.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she came in and said, let's leave the room right now, because the Germans are coming back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was only 7 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said to her, get out of the house because you are black, black crow-- you're bringing back bad news.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They never come back after 5 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Didn't take five minutes, people were running in all directions and the German came back, and took that time maybe 500 or 600 people, and sent them to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Definitely intuition.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
